---
import Triangle from "@icons/triangle-yellow.svg";
---

<section>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Soccer Coaching with Purpose</h2>
        <p class="p-block">
            Soccer Every Day Academy was built to give every player the chance
            to grow. Whether you’re kicking a ball for the first time or chasing
            a higher level of performance, we offer coaching that’s tailored,
            professional and built for long-term development.
        </p>
        <p class="p-block">
            Our head coach brings experience from working across multiple
            continents, combining football knowledge with a background in sports
            science. We now work closely with Terrigal FC and Terrigal
            Development Centre to support players all across the Central Coast.
        </p>
        <div class="mission">
            <div class="mission-header">
                <h3>Our Mission at Soccer Everyday Academy</h3>
                <Triangle />
            </div>
            <p>
                To help players of all levels unlock their potential through
                quality coaching, individualised training and a deep love for
                the game.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    h2 {
        background-color: var(--dark);
        color: white;
        padding: 1rem 1rem 0.8rem 1rem;
        font-size: 2rem;
    }
    .container {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 2rem;
    }

    .mission {
        background-color: var(--dark);
        color: white;
        padding: 1rem;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
    }
    .mission-header {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
    }
    h3 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
</style>
